{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"ida88f24d8-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s1095g"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1095g"},"text":"§ 1095g.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" TRICARE program: waiver of recoupment of erroneous payments caused by administrative error","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"ida88f24d9-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s1095g/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Waiver of Recoupment","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"The Secretary of Defense may waive recoupment from an individual who has benefitted from an erroneous TRICARE payment in a case in which each of the following applies:","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"ida88f24da-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s1095g/a/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" The payment was made because of an administrative error by an employee of the Department of Defense or a contractor under the TRICARE program.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"ida88f24db-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s1095g/a/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" The individual (or in the case of a minor, the parent or guardian of the individual) had a good faith, reasonable belief that the individual was entitled to the benefit of such payment under this chapter.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"ida88f24dc-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s1095g/a/3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3"},"text":"(3)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" The individual relied on the expectation of such entitlement.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"ida88f24dd-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s1095g/a/4"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"4"},"text":"(4)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" The Secretary determines that a waiver of recoupment of such payment is necessary to prevent an injustice.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"ida88f24de-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s1095g/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Responsibility of Contractor","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"In any case in which the Secretary waives recoupment under subsection (a) and the administrative error was on the part of a contractor under the TRICARE program, the Secretary shall, consistent with the requirements and procedures of the applicable contract, impose financial responsibility on the contractor for the erroneous payment.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"ida88f24df-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s1095g/c"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"c"},"text":"(c)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" ","children":[{"tag":"inline","attrib":{},"text":"Finality of Determinations","children":[],"tail":".—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"Any determination by the Secretary under this section to waive or decline to waive recoupment under subsection (a) is a final determination and shall not be subject to appeal or judicial review.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"ida88f24e0-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":"(Added ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/114/92/dA/tVII/s711/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 114–92, div. A, title VII, § 711(a)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2015-11-25"},"text":"Nov. 25, 2015","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/129/864"},"text":"129 Stat. 864","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
